
You can use these scripts by drag'n drop into Poky Notepad (two-letter-code "Pn") and execute (File -> Run Python Module in Poky Notepad).
Dropping into the non-text area of Poky Notepad will load the file. Simply copy-and-paste will do as well.

Please watch: https://youtu.be/tGh4CmpJeXE

We plan to include these scripts in the Poky package when major updates occur.

